# Studio app config (`apps/studio/*.ts`)

- **`sanity.config.ts`:** Plugins **`structureTool`** + **`visionTool`** only; project id/dataset from `SANITY_STUDIO_*` env.
- **`structure.ts`:** Document lists and **`siteSettings`** singleton id — keep ids stable (`siteSettings`) for GROQ in the web app.
- Changing titles/icons here does not change the web — but reordering or hiding schema types affects editors.
